      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，混合云场景。那Azure这边需要展开到什么程度？我看到有Resource Group、VNet这些，是要画成子图(subgraph)的形式吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
