      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "On-Prem写\"On-Prem (VyOS + VMs)\"，VyOS是那边的路由器。它和Azure VNet之间是VPN连接，用双向箭头还是单向？",
      "elements_involved": [
